{
  "stem": "24614.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you become aware of what was going on, besides visitors?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the youth group.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One night, we had a meeting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had an ulam, U-L-A-M, a meeting room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our leader was telling us about what Hitler is doing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was saying that maybe one day, all of us will have to leave even Antwerp, Belgium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he told us about the Youth, Y-O-U-T-H, Aliyah, A-L-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how would I spell Aliyah?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A-L-O?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A-L-I-- my god, I can't spell anymore-- Y-A, Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were planning already, the-- in, in Palestine then, there were leaders who were planning to bring to Palestine young boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my leader, who was in charge of us in Antwerp, left end of 1939 with the Youth Aliyah.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First, they were going to France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they were going to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they were smuggled into Palestine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was one of the stops.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My brother wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother never-- she said, you're so young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We-- I can't let you go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in 1941, one group went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they caught them on the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They stopped to eat with the-- across the street a German barrack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the Germans caught them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were very safe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they-- my daddy-- I heard my daddy say many, many times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My uncle came from Czechoslovakia in 1939.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he begged my father to go to Palestine with him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember my uncle-- my father saying, it won't happen in Belgium, not in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
